---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Cristian Palacios | Portfolio Engineer & RPA Developer">
	<main>
		<section id="hero">
			<h1>Cristian Palacios</h1>
			<p class="role">
				Ingeniero de Portafolios TI | Desarrollador RPA & Cloud
			</p>
			<div class="status-badge">
				<span class="dot"></span> Disponible para nuevos desafíos
			</div>
			<div class="social-links">
				<a
					href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/cpalacios-borquez/"
					target="_blank"
					title="LinkedIn"
				>
					<i class="devicon-linkedin-plain"></i>
				</a>
				<a
					href="https://github.com/cpalacios-dev"
					target="_blank"
					title="GitHub"
				>
					<i class="devicon-github-original"></i>
				</a>
				<a
					href="mailto:cpalacios.borquez@gmail.com"
					title="Enviar Email"
				>
					<i class="devicon-google-plain"></i>
				</a>
			</div>

			<div class="description">
				Especialista en modernización tecnológica mediante el diseño de
				<strong>arquitecturas escalables en la nube (GCP)</strong> y la implementación
				de modelos <strong>Robot as a Service (RaaS)</strong>. Lidero la
				convergencia entre la visión estratégica y la solidez técnica.
			</div>

			<div class="tech-ticker">
				<div class="ticker-content">
					<i class="devicon-python-plain"></i>
					<i class="devicon-googlecloud-plain"></i>
					<i class="devicon-docker-plain"></i>
					<i class="devicon-playwright-plain"></i>

					<svg
						class="custom-icon"
						viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						fill="currentColor"
					>
						<path
							d="M12.522 17.153h-1.045v-4.108c0-1.228-.686-1.921-1.844-1.921-1.12 0-1.821.693-1.821 1.921v4.108H6.767v-6.398h1.045v.859c.403-.642 1.03-.986 1.918-.986 1.701 0 2.792 1.052 2.792 2.822v3.703zm6.278-3.576c0 2.21-1.687 3.702-3.896 3.702-2.217 0-3.881-1.492-3.881-3.702 0-2.201 1.664-3.687 3.881-3.687 2.21 0 3.896 1.486 3.896 3.687zm-1.09 0c0-1.635-1.187-2.731-2.806-2.731-1.627 0-2.8 1.096-2.8 2.731 0 1.642 1.173 2.747 2.8 2.747 1.62 0 2.806-1.105 2.806-2.747zM5.2 6.847V17.153H4.155V6.847H5.2zM15.433 6.847v1.896h-1.612v1.545h1.612v4.202c0 1.747.933 2.664 2.664 2.664h.702v-.896h-.567c-1.142 0-1.754-.567-1.754-1.768V10.288h2.321V8.743h-2.321V6.847h-1.045z"
						></path>
					</svg>

					<svg
						class="custom-icon"
						viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						fill="currentColor"
					>
						<path
							d="M12 0L2.4 5.4v13.2L12 24l9.6-5.4V5.4L12 0zm7.2 17.4l-7.2 4.05-7.2-4.05V6.6L12 2.55l7.2 4.05v10.8zM12 7.2L8.4 9.15v5.7l3.6 1.95 3.6-1.95v-5.7L12 7.2z"
						></path>
					</svg>

					<svg
						class="custom-icon"
						viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						fill="currentColor"
					>
						<path
							d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5-10-5-10 5z"
						></path>
					</svg>

					<svg
						class="custom-icon"
						viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						fill="currentColor"
					>
						<path
							d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm0 18c-4.41 0-8-3.59-8-8s3.59-8 8-8 8 3.59 8 8-3.59 8-8 8zm-1-13h2v6h-2zm0 8h2v2h-2z"
						></path>
					</svg>

					<i class="devicon-azuresqldatabase-plain"></i>
					<i class="devicon-github-original"></i>
					<i class="devicon-dot-net-plain"></i>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="expertise">
			<h2>Stack Tecnológico y de Gestión</h2>
			<div class="expertise-grid">
				<div class="skill-item">
					<i class="devicon-googlecloud-plain colored"></i>
					<span
						><strong>Cloud & DevOps:</strong> GCP (Cloud Run), Docker,
						Arquitectura Serverless.</span
					>
				</div>
				<div class="skill-item">
					<i class="devicon-python-plain colored"></i>
					<span
						><strong>Backend & Automatización:</strong> Python, Playwright,
						orquestación con Appian y n8n.</span
					>
				</div>
				<div class="skill-item">
					<i class="devicon-jira-plain colored"></i>
					<span
						><strong>Gestión Estratégica:</strong> VDD, Priorización WSJF/RICE,
						Metodologías Ágiles (Scrum).</span
					>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="raas-architecture">
			<div class="raas-container">
				<div class="raas-badge">Core Expertise</div>
				<h2>Arquitectura RaaS (Robot as a Service)</h2>
				<p>
					Diseño de microservicios transaccionales bajo modelo <strong
						>RaaS</strong
					>, utilizando
					<strong>Python</strong> y <strong>Playwright</strong>.
					Desplegados sobre infraestructura serverless en <strong
						>Google Cloud Platform (GCP - Cloud Run)</strong
					> para garantizar alta disponibilidad y escalabilidad masiva.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="proyectos">
			<h2>Experiencia de Alto Impacto</h2>
			<div class="project-grid">
				<article class="project-card">
					<header>
						<span class="company">SURA AFP CAPITAL</span>
						<h3>Modelo Robot as a Service (RaaS)</h3>
					</header>
					<p>
						Desarrollo de microservicios transaccionales en <strong
							>Cloud Run</strong
						> e integración de
						<strong>IA (OCR/NLP)</strong> para la gestión automatizada
						de nóminas críticas.
					</p>
					<div class="tags">
						<span>GCP</span><span>Python</span><span>IA</span>
					</div>
				</article>

				<article class="project-card">
					<header>
						<span class="company">CLARO CHILE S.A.</span>
						<h3>Modernización e Integración</h3>
					</header>
					<p>
						Liderazgo en la integración de sistemas legacy mediante <strong
							>APIs REST/SOAP</strong
						>, mejorando la interoperabilidad y experiencia de
						usuario.
					</p>
					<div class="tags">
						<span>APIs</span><span>Interoperabilidad</span><span
							>Liderazgo</span
						>
					</div>
				</article>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="vdd-strategy">
			<h2>Estrategia VDD (Value Driven Delivery)</h2>
			<p>
				Priorización de backlog basada en modelos matemáticos de
				eficiencia:
			</p>
			<div class="vdd-table-container">
				<table>
					<thead>
						<tr>
							<th>Modelo</th>
							<th>Aplicación</th>
							<th>Meta</th>
						</tr>
					</thead>
					<tbody>
						<tr>
							<td><strong>WSJF</strong></td>
							<td>Costo del retraso</td>
							<td>Agilidad Financiera</td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<td><strong>RICE / ICE</strong></td>
							<td>Impacto vs Esfuerzo</td>
							<td>ROI de Automatización</td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<td><strong>MoSCoW</strong></td>
							<td>Clasificación Crítica</td>
							<td>Cumplimiento de Plazos</td>
						</tr>
					</tbody>
				</table>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="certificaciones">
			<h2>Certificaciones y Especialización</h2>
			<div class="cert-grid">
				<div class="cert-card gold">
					<div class="cert-header">
						<i class="devicon-blueprism-plain colored"></i>
						<span>Oficial</span>
					</div>
					<h4>Blue Prism Certified Developer</h4>
					<p>SS&C Blue Prism | 2020</p>
				</div>

				<div class="cert-card academy">
					<div class="cert-header">
						<i class="devicon-appian-plain colored"></i>
						<span>Academy 2026</span>
					</div>
					<h4>Appian Developer</h4>
					<p>Appian Academy | Low-Code Automation</p>
				</div>

				<div class="cert-card academy">
					<div class="cert-header">
						<i class="devicon-uipath-plain colored"></i>
						<span>Academy</span>
					</div>
					<h4>RPA Developer Foundation</h4>
					<p>UiPath Academy | EY Consulting</p>
				</div>

				<div class="cert-card tech">
					<div class="cert-header">
						<i class="devicon-python-plain colored"></i>
						<span>Curso</span>
					</div>
					<h4>Análisis de Datos con Python</h4>
					<p>Desafío Latam | Oct 2025</p>
					<span class="id">ID: omfqaqs5m0</span>
				</div>

				<div class="cert-card tech">
					<div class="cert-header">
						<i class="devicon-redhat-plain colored"></i>
						<span>Especialización</span>
					</div>
					<h4>Red Hat OpenShift Training</h4>
					<p>Red Hat | Contenedores y Kubernetes</p>
				</div>

				<div class="cert-card tech">
					<div class="cert-header">
						<i class="devicon-microsoft-plain colored"></i>
						<span>Formación</span>
					</div>
					<h4>Power Automate Desktop / Cloud</h4>
					<p>Udemy | Curso Completo RPA</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		<section id="trayectoria">
			<h2>Trayectoria y Formación</h2>
			<div class="timeline">
				<div class="timeline-item">
					<span class="year">2026</span>
					<h4>Ingeniero de Portafolios TI & RPA</h4>
					<p>
						Kibernum | Especialista en automatización para SURA AFP
						Capital.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="timeline-item">
					<span class="year">2024</span>
					<h4>Posgrado en Gestión de Portafolios</h4>
					<p>
						Tecnológico de Monterrey | Especialización en Value
						Driven Delivery.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="timeline-item">
					<span class="year">2023 - 2025</span>
					<h4>Líder de Proyectos de Integración</h4>
					<p>Claro Chile | Gestión de modernización tecnológica.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="timeline-item">
					<span class="year">2020</span>
					<h4>Ingeniería en Informática</h4>
					<p>IPCHILE | Gestión de Sistemas y Procesos.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="contacto">
			<div class="cta-container">
				<a
					href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/cpalacios-borquez/"
					target="_blank"
					class="btn linkedin">LinkedIn</a
				>
				<a href="mailto:cpalacios.borquez@gmail.com" class="btn mail"
					>Email</a
				>
				<a href="/cv_cpalacios.pdf" download class="btn cv"
					>Descargar CV</a
				>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
<style>
	/* 1. Configuración de Contenedor Principal */
	main {
		margin: auto;
		padding: 2rem;
		width: 800px;
		max-width: calc(100% - 2rem);
		color: #ffffff;
		line-height: 1.6;
		font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
		overflow-x: hidden;
	}

	/* 2. Tipografía y Títulos */
	h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		margin-bottom: 0;
		background: linear-gradient(45deg, #4f39fa, #da62c4);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
	}
	.role {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		color: #a3a3a3;
		margin-top: 0.5rem;
	}
	section {
		margin-top: 4rem;
	}
	strong {
		color: #da62c4;
	}

	/* 3. Limpieza Global de Enlaces */
	a {
		text-decoration: none !important;
		outline: none;
	}

	/* 4. Ticker de Tecnologías (Contenido al ancho del main) */
	.tech-ticker {
		width: 100%;
		overflow: hidden;
		background: #1e1e1e;
		padding: 1.5rem 0;
		margin-top: 2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border: 1px solid #333;
	}
	.ticker-content {
		display: flex;
		width: max-content;
		animation: scroll 30s linear infinite;
	}
	.ticker-content i {
		font-size: 2.2rem;
		margin: 0 2rem;
		color: #666;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}
	@keyframes scroll {
		0% {
			transform: translateX(0);
		}
		100% {
			transform: translateX(-50%);
		}
	}

	/* 5. Grids y Tarjetas Generales */
	.expertise-grid {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1rem;
	}
	.project-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}
	.skill-item,
	.project-card {
		background: #1e1e1e;
		border: 1px solid #333;
		border-radius: 12px;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		transition:
			transform 0.2s ease,
			border-color 0.2s ease;
	}
	.project-card:hover {
		transform: scale(1.02);
		border-color: #4f39fa;
	}

	/* 6. Sección de Certificaciones (Bordes Definidos por Color) */
	.cert-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}
	.cert-card {
		background: #1e1e1e;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border: 1px solid #333;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		transition:
			transform 0.3s ease,
			border-color 0.3s ease,
			box-shadow 0.3s ease;
		position: relative;
	}
	.cert-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
	}

	/* Variantes de Color para Certificaciones */
	.cert-card.gold {
		border: 1px solid #ffd700;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.1);
	}
	.cert-card.gold:hover {
		box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.2);
	}
	.cert-card.gold span {
		background: #ffd700;
		color: #000;
		font-weight: bold;
	}

	.cert-card.academy {
		border: 1px solid #4f39fa;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(79, 57, 250, 0.1);
	}
	.cert-card.academy:hover {
		box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(79, 57, 250, 0.2);
	}
	.cert-card.academy span {
		background: #4f39fa;
		color: #fff;
	}

	.cert-card.tech {
		border: 1px solid #da62c4;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(218, 98, 196, 0.1);
	}
	.cert-card.tech:hover {
		box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(218, 98, 196, 0.2);
	}
	.cert-card.tech span {
		background: #da62c4;
		color: #fff;
	}

	.cert-header {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: center;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	.cert-header i {
		font-size: 1.8rem;
	}
	.cert-header span {
		font-size: 0.65rem;
		padding: 2px 8px;
		border-radius: 4px;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}
	.cert-card .id {
		font-size: 0.7rem;
		color: #4ade80;
		margin-top: auto;
		padding-top: 1rem;
		font-family: monospace;
	}

	/* 7. Secciones Especiales (RaaS, VDD, Timeline) */
	.raas-container {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e1e1e 0%, #252525 100%);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 16px;
		border: 1px solid #4f39fa;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}
	.raas-badge {
		background: #4f39fa;
		color: white;
		font-size: 0.7rem;
		padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
		border-radius: 20px;
		display: inline-block;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		font-weight: bold;
	}
	table {
		width: 100%;
		border-collapse: collapse;
		margin-top: 1rem;
		background: #1e1e1e;
		border-radius: 8px;
		overflow: hidden;
	}
	th,
	td {
		padding: 12px;
		text-align: left;
		border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
	}
	th {
		background-color: #252525;
		color: #da62c4;
	}

	.timeline {
		border-left: 2px solid #4f39fa;
		margin-left: 1rem;
		padding-left: 2rem;
	}
	.timeline-item {
		position: relative;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
	}
	.timeline-item::before {
		content: "";
		position: absolute;
		left: calc(-2rem - 6px);
		top: 5px;
		width: 10px;
		height: 10px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: #da62c4;
	}

	/* 8. Footer y Socials */
	.cta-container {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		justify-content: center;
		margin-top: 5rem;
		padding-bottom: 5rem;
	}
	.btn {
		padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		font-weight: bold;
		transition: 0.2s;
	}
	.linkedin {
		background: #0077b5;
		color: white;
	}
	.mail {
		background: #4f39fa;
		color: white;
	}
	.cv {
		border: 1px solid #da62c4;
		color: #da62c4;
	}

	.social-links {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-top: 1rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}
	.social-links a {
		color: #a3a3a3;
		font-size: 1.8rem;
		transition: 0.3s;
		display: inline-block;
	}
	.social-links a:hover {
		color: #da62c4;
		transform: translateY(-3px);
	}

	.status-badge {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		color: #4ade80;
		margin-top: 0.5rem;
	}
	.dot {
		width: 8px;
		height: 8px;
		background-color: #4ade80;
		border-radius: 50%;
		animation: pulse 2s infinite;
	}
	@keyframes pulse {
		0%,
		100% {
			opacity: 1;
		}
		50% {
			opacity: 0.4;
		}
	}
	/* Estilo para los SVG manuales en el ticker */
    .custom-icon {
        width: 2.2rem; /* Mismo tamaño que los i de Devicon */
        height: 2.2rem;
        margin: 0 2rem;
        color: #666;
        flex-shrink: 0;
        transition: color 0.3s ease;
        display: inline-block;
        vertical-align: middle;
    }

    .custom-icon:hover {
        color: #da62c4; /* El color fucsia de tu marca */
    }
</style>
